title: Trailer Trash Five
description:
Another inimitable issue of Roy Tompkin's Trailer Trash.

Lovingly prepared, squared and gently sharpened while preserving the yellow paper that befits a comic of this vintage. On a retina screen, it even better than having the actual comic in front of you. Really!

Is this where Seth McFarlane got the idea to draw Stewie Griffin with a football shaped head?
